---
title: Rigatoni with Chicken & Mushroom Ragù with Garlic, Rosemary & Parsley
description: Here’s the weeknight vegan dinner idea you’ve been coveting! If you ever miss the meaty joy that is a ragù, miss it no more with this gem our chefs dreamed up. Earthy, meaty button mushrooms make the perfect stand-in for ground meat. Simmer those mushrooms with tomatoes, onion, and garlic, then drape the sauce over chewy mouthfuls of rigatoni and, really, what’s to miss? You’ll be craving this veg version from now on.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/63a327947d50ca4d660f3394-aa0c572b.jpg
